title: @OspreyMTEN Completes Day Two at USTA/ITA Regionals
text: 6' 3" Jr. GAINESVILLE, Fla. â€“ All seven members of the North Florida Men's Tennis team were in action Friday at the USTA/ITA Southeast Regionals in Gainesville, Fla. "We let a big opportunity slip away to have a flawless doubles session this afternoon. We had the number team in the nation up against the ropes but let them claw their way back in," said head coach . "However there were many great aspects overall in doubles that was very pleasing. In singles it was great to see Julian get another ranked win. Jonathan also had a great gritty performance to beat his opponent."
